Light is coming from the upper right, casting pronounced shadows to the lower left of the raised material and the edges of the indentation. These shadows give the image depth and highlight the texture and the form of the letter. The background surface has a uniform appearance of densely packed granules.

The overall color palette is dominated by shades of gray, with lighter tones on the well-lit parts of the surface and darker tones and black in the shadows within the indentation and cast onto the surface. The letter "H" is centrally placed within the frame and occupies a significant portion of the image.
